<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Thank You for Your Review - Momos Buddies</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0; padding:0; background-color:#f5f5f5; font-family:'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;">

  <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color:#f5f5f5; padding: 30px 0;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center">

        <!-- Email Card -->
        <table width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="max-width:600px; width:100%; background:#ffffff; border-radius:16px; overflow:hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.10);">

          <!-- Header with gradient -->
          <tr>
            <td style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d14517ff 0%, #C0392B 100%); padding: 36px 40px; text-align:center;">
              <%= image_tag 'logo.png', alt: 'Momos Buddies', style: 'width:110px; height:110px; border-radius:50%; border: 4px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.35); display:block; margin: 0 auto 12px auto;' %>
              <h1 style="margin:0; color:#ffffff; font-size:26px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.5px;">Momos Buddies</h1>
              <p style="margin:4px 0 0; color:rgba(255,255,240,0.88); font-size:13px; font-style:italic;">Har bite mein dosti ka taste 🥟</p>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Body -->
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 36px 44px 28px;">

              <p style="margin:0 0 10px; font-size:17px; color:#333; font-weight:600;">
                Dear <%= @name %>,
              </p>

              <p style="margin:0 0 18px; font-size:15px; color:#555; line-height:1.8;">
                Thank you so much for taking the time to share your valuable review with us! 🙏<br>
                Your feedback means the world to us and truly helps us grow and serve you better.
              </p>

              <p style="margin:0 0 18px; font-size:15px; color:#555; line-height:1.8;">
                At <strong style="color:#E8501A;">Momos Buddies</strong>, every opinion matters — you are the reason we strive to make every bite more delicious than the last.
              </p>

              <!-- Divider -->
              <hr style="border:none; border-top: 2px dashed #f0d0c0; margin: 24px 0;">

              <!-- Growth Highlights Section -->
              <p style="margin:0 0 16px; font-size:17px; font-weight:700; color:#C0392B;">🚀 Exciting Things Coming Your Way!</p>

              <!-- Card 1 -->
              <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-bottom:14px;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="background:#fff5f0; border-left: 4px solid #E8501A; border-radius:8px; padding:14px 18px;">
                    <p style="margin:0 0 4px; font-size:14px; font-weight:700; color:#E8501A;">🛵 Online Ordering & Delivery</p>
                    <p style="margin:0; font-size:13px; color:#555; line-height:1.7;">
                      We are rolling out a fast and convenient online ordering platform — so your favourite momos are just a few taps away!
                    </p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <!-- Card 2 -->
              <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-bottom:14px;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="background:#fff5f0; border-left: 4px solid #C0392B; border-radius:8px; padding:14px 18px;">
                    <p style="margin:0 0 4px; font-size:14px; font-weight:700; color:#C0392B;">🌟 New Menu Innovations</p>
                    <p style="margin:0; font-size:13px; color:#555; line-height:1.7;">
                      Get ready for exciting new flavours, fusion varieties, and seasonal specials crafted with love — straight from our kitchen to your heart.
                    </p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <!-- Card 3 -->
              <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-bottom:14px;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="background:#fff5f0; border-left: 4px solid #E8501A; border-radius:8px; padding:14px 18px;">
                    <p style="margin:0 0 4px; font-size:14px; font-weight:700; color:#E8501A;">📍 Expanding Locations</p>
                    <p style="margin:0; font-size:13px; color:#555; line-height:1.7;">
                      We are expanding to new locations so more people can enjoy the authentic taste of Momos Buddies — stay tuned!
                    </p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <!-- Card 4 -->
              <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-bottom:14px;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="background:#fff5f0; border-left: 4px solid #C0392B; border-radius:8px; padding:14px 18px;">
                    <p style="margin:0 0 4px; font-size:14px; font-weight:700; color:#C0392B;">🎁 Loyalty Rewards Program</p>
                    <p style="margin:0; font-size:13px; color:#555; line-height:1.7;">
                      As a token of appreciation, we are launching a Loyalty Program — earn points with every order and redeem exciting rewards and discounts!
                    </p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <!-- Card 5 -->
              <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-bottom:8px;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="background:#fff5f0; border-left: 4px solid #E8501A; border-radius:8px; padding:14px 18px;">
                    <p style="margin:0 0 4px; font-size:14px; font-weight:700; color:#E8501A;">📱 Social Community</p>
                    <p style="margin:0; font-size:13px; color:#555; line-height:1.7;">
                      Join our growing community on Instagram & Facebook! Share your momo moments, tag us, and be part of the Momos Buddies family.
                    </p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <hr style="border:none; border-top: 2px dashed #f0d0c0; margin: 24px 0;">

              <p style="margin:0 0 10px; font-size:15px; color:#555; line-height:1.8;">
                Once again, thank you for being such a wonderful part of our journey. Your support motivates us every single day to do better and grow further. 💛
              </p>

              <p style="margin:0; font-size:15px; color:#555; line-height:1.8;">
                Warm regards,<br>
                <strong style="color:#E8501A;">The Momos Buddies Team</strong><br>
                <span style="font-size:13px; color:#999;">📧 momos.buddies@gmail.com</span>
              </p>

            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Footer -->
          <tr>
            <td style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #E8501A 0%, #C0392B 100%); padding: 20px 40px; text-align:center;">
              <p style="margin:0; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.85); font-size:12px; line-height:1.7;">
                © <%= Date.today.year %> Momos Buddies &nbsp;|&nbsp;
                <a href="https://momosbuddies.com" style="color:#FFE58F; text-decoration:none;">momosbuddies.com</a>
                &nbsp;|&nbsp; Har bite mein dosti ka taste 🥟
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

        </table>
        <!-- End Email Card -->

      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>

</body>
</html>
